(- audio is the main audio scorer, while the spectrogram and sequence branches are secondary stabilizers.) Tj
T*
(- image_dl is currently the strongest image bundle and should be treated as the default image scorer.) Tj
T*
(- comorbidity is intentionally last in the stack and should be retrained after text, audio, and image stabilize.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
